Okolea International recently sponsored a golf day at the Limuru Country Club to create more awareness among golfers of its products and services. The event attracted 150 golfers and guests. Okolea COO Cosmas Mulumba and director George Njuguna led top management in attending the event, which will be held annually. Okolea is a fast-growing fin-tech that uses information technology to provide financial solutions to customers who are unbanked.Â It has a subsidiary company known as Eneza Telecom, which offers software as a service, allowing small businesses to automate their processes affordably.